column5: Hi everyone, At one time I ran across a web site that listed boat launches for parts of Ontario, but can't seem to find it now. Does anyone know what the site is and if they could pass it on to me it would be much appreciated . Many thanks in advance Sunchaser81
This one is pretty good.  Just click  the area you want to see from the list on the left.  http://www.boatlaunches.ca/index.php?optio...4&Itemid=55
Thanks Roy It does look good, I will play around with it. sunchaser81
